{"type": "article", "id": 1291, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2014-06-27T15:16:51Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 1328, "name": "灯"}, {"id": 1363, "name": "人体彩绘"}, {"id": 752, "name": "宠物"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 11, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604215539AJNVr6dSy5Rjmuti.jpg", "contents": "\n<!--?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" standalone=\"no\"?-->\n<b>1. Banana Cone </b> \r\n<div>\r\n\t在公共场所清洁过后的地板上总会看到一个黄色警示牌，这款黄色香蕉皮造型的警示牌在颜色和造型上都恰当地提示了路人：“路面湿滑，谨防摔倒”。不过，一个香蕉皮也要 120 美金 ，在 <a href=\"http://www.ebay.com/itm/Banana-Safety-Cones-3-Pack-with-3-Additional-Stems-/281352652222?\" target=\"_blank\">Ebay</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Wet-Floor-Sign-Cones-Banana/dp/B00FADYTAE/ref=sr_1_11?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1393298117&amp;sr=8-11&amp;keywords=wet+floor+cone%20\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon</a> 都有卖。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215527hKsw5mTDoZRjyBHF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<b>2. Body Painting by John Poppleton</b> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t人体彩绘见过不少，但艺术家 John Poppleton 把自然和人体结合的彩绘在照片负片的拍摄效果下，营造出了不一样的感觉。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215528ocT7Bd8sKDHwxO5l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215528rbUS1LTpgZGeMkdR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215529ykPvIj1YbJh4NCuB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215529L3WXvyDopPRKjtq6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215530xBX0HjzpWnJZ1qyL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.378125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215530wYkOygQM6IXUqvVS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215531worR3MH08tJiTNAZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042155312bWI9QrxijodzwP8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215532G2XfwDNplJITzt39.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<b>3. Lumiosf </b> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t换一个角度看世界，一切可能都会不一样。换一个角度看书，书也不再是书的样子。这盏灯的灵感来源于打开的书本，当以往只有 180 度铺张开来的书被 360 度展开，每页纸被凝固定格时，原本的平面书也变作立体的灯。充电后，随身携带着这本小书，在需要光源的时候打开就使用。今天开始发售，可惜只在日本。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215533N4d9QqOgBM8uDHej.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215533spArOTYoxif32dKZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<b>4. Kittyo </b> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t不少人虽然工作忙碌，但还是时刻惦记着家里的小宠物。现在，Kittyo 推出的远程 Kittyo 玩乐工具能让主人通过手机应用程序和家里的小宠物远程互动。其中它带有的摄像头能看到仪器面前的宠物，通过在手机桌面上点击地面的不同位置，仪器上会有激光光线射出，让宠物们可以随着你点的位置去追逐，除了视频还可以和小宠物对话。嗯，还暗藏了小点心奖励哦。现在 <a href=\"http://kittyo.com\" target=\"_blank\">Kittyo 官网</a>接受预定了，预计 11 月就能正式发售。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215534hNbBFdJEZc4fH0mA.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060421553578Qkwx4MVIOftWSb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.596875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215535os3AZJNl6Egj0HQa.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.578125\" data-format=\"png\"><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<b>5. Magnetic Target for Keys</b> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t钥匙这种小玩意儿总是会在进门后随手乱扔，对于不少人来说，出门前翻箱倒柜地找钥匙是时有发生的事，而忘带钥匙也是常见。如果门边放一块磁铁板，进门一贴，总会再出门的时候能找到。更何况它是个靶心造型，要忽略它也不是件容易的事。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042155361NKyZIgFGt4BD5lA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215537ARfb35OGyuo9MVFd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215537WyIfQO2kTmlN05sw.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-format=\"png\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215538evIR2xiDdpoLBgWf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.521875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}